1.title: Cowboy
1.plot: Mutt and Stuff's new student, Cowboy is a bossy dog. Calvin helps Cowboy see how his actions make the other dogs feel, and he becomes a well-loved part of the pack.

2.title: Bring in Da Skunk
2.plot: Noodles disguises his friend, Olive the Skunk, as a dog to show the class that they shouldn't judge a friend by their fur.

3.title: Roller Dogs
3.plot: Mutt and Stuff goes to a Roller Rink, but Calvin doesn't know how to roller skate. Calvin gets some help from Dr. Kristina to become a skating star.

4.title: Doggy Adventure Day
4.plot: The Mutt & Stuff dogs play jungle adventure games! Even though the games prove to be a big challenge, the dogs learn the value of never giving up with Calvin's encouragement and supportive guidance.

5.title: Sit, Stay, Stand Up!
5.plot: Calvin invites comedian Wally Whiskers to Mutt & Stuff for Junior Shades' birthday. When Wally's cat-themed jokes fall flat, Calvin helps him learn all about dog behavior, and he becomes a doggy joke-telling pro!

6.title: Basketball Dogs vs. The Harlem Globetrotters
6.plot: The Harlem Globetrotters play Mutt & Stuff in a game of basketball! Stuff isn't worried, because with his lucky charm, Murray the Walrus, he never misses a shot.

7.title: H.R. Pufnstuf's Happy Tree Jamboree
7.plot: H.R. Pufnstuf is coming to Mutt & Stuff to celebrate the Bloomy Tree Jamboree! The Trees' flowers haven't bloomed yet, so Stuff and the dogs help figure out the special surprise that makes the Trees bloom into flowers!

8.title: Putt & Stuff
8.plot: Mutt & Stuff goes mini golfing! But when Noodles the Mouse secretly helps Sunny win at each hole, he learns that it's best to practice hard to learn a new skill.

9.title: Annie to the Rescue!
9.plot: Mutt & Stuff is celebrating Dude's graduation, but when Dude goes missing, Annie the Animal Rescuer shows up and uses her skills to track down the missing dog!

10.title: Doggy Mermaid Island
10.plot: Mutt & Stuff's new student, Pearl, is half dog, half fish, and totally shy! The class comes to Doggy Mermaid Island to help Pearl overcome her first-day-of-school jitters!

11.title: Grandma's Day Off
11.plot: It's Grandma Day at Mutt & Stuff! Calvin calls Buddy Sitandshake, professional dog sitter, to puppy sit Grandma's puppies. When Buddy gets overwhelmed with the big responsibility, he learns to ask for help!

12.title: Woof Out!
12.plot: Buddy Sitandshake, a professional dog sitter, competes in new doggy game show "Woof Out!" With the help of his Mutt & Stuff buddies, Buddy wins the grand prize, defeating his opponent Peter Poodlerino!

13.title: Doggy Dining Disaster
13.plot: The Mutt & Stuff class helps a doggy chef open a restaurant in the school! The dogs must work together to impress the food critic, Theodore Von Barkerman.

14.title: The Wag 4 Rock Concert
14.plot: Stuff and the dogs are putting on a rock concert, and when they need a singer, they turn to Gabi Groomer who happens to have a great voice. With encouragement from the whole pack, she overcomes her stage fright and sings with the pups.

15.title: A Chew Toy Fairy-Tail
15.plot: When Stuff breaks his favorite chew toy, a tiny flying "Chew Toy Fairy" arrives to the toy. But when her magic wand breaks, Calvin and the dogs have to help her find her magic powers again so she can fix doggy toy all over the world.

16.title: Hocus Puppy Pocus
16.plot: When Stuff uses his new magic book to perform tricks, he accidentally turns Calvin into a chicken. He needs the help of his favorite magician, Irving the Enchanted to save the day.

17.title: Dog Star Challenge
17.plot: A famous doggy website is having a competition: send in a video of the best action dog. Zippy is ready to compete, but then his identical brothers Speedy and Peppy show up. It's sibling rivalry on Mutt and Stuff.

18.title: Construction Dogs!
18.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

19.title: Hop Dog
19.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

20.title: The Happy Hallowoof Party
20.plot: Calvin and the dogs are having a big Halloween costume party, but when Cuddles doesn't get an invitation in the mailbox, the sad pup thinks he wasn't invited. Lucky for Cuddles, Annie The Animal Rescuer shows up looking for lost baby bunnies, and she vows to help find the missing invitation too!

21.title: The Woof Zone!
21.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

22.title: Super Hero Dogs
22.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

23.title: The Dog Boat!
23.plot: Mutt and Stuff goes on a doggy cruise. But when Stuff hurts his ankle, he has to find new ways to have fun on the ship.

24.title: Surprise Birthday Balloon Bash!
24.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

25.title: Twin Day!
25.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

26.title: Get Up and Bark!
26.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

27.title: CannonDOG Run!
27.plot: Set in a unique school for dogs,Mutt & Stuff stars Calvin Millan (son of Cesar Millan, "The Dog Whisperer") interacting with a cast of real dogs and puppets.

28.title: Pixie I Shrunk the Class!
28.plot: Little Pixie is sad about being the smallest dog at Mutt and Stuff. Pixie tries to use a grow ray to make herself bigger, but accidentally shrinks Calvin and the rest of the dogs.

29.title: Woofing Nine to Five!
29.plot: It's Career day at Mutt and Stuff. Stuff tries to figure out which career he could do when a rescue dog, sled dog and a seeing-eye dog come to visit.

30.title: Dog Submarine!
30.plot: It's baseball day at Mutt and Stuff. Zippy hits a home run and sends the ball to the bottom of the ocean. The dogs ride a submarine to find it, while also making some new underwater friends.

31.title: Doggy Gymnastics!
31.plot: Olympic Medalist Simone Biles comes to Mutt and Stuff and invites Calvin and the dogs to join her Gymnastics Team. But after the dogs forget to pack important items for the competition, Calvin teaches them a lesson about being prepared.

32.title: Doggy Safari!
32.plot: Calvin and the dogs go on a real, wild animal safari with their Safari Guide, Sally Safari. But when Sally gets bummed out that she can't find any animals, the dogs help boost her up and search with her.

33.title: Choo Choo Trouble!
33.plot: It's class movie day at Mutt and Stuff, but when a determined railroad builder decides to build a train through Mutt and Stuff, Calvin and the class must figure out a way to save their school.

1.title: Hip-Hop Dogs
1.plot: Calvin helps one of his doggy students cope with missing his owner while he's at school. Even better, Calvin helps the owner when she needs back-up dancers at her dance performance. Cue the Mutt & Stuff hip hop dog dancers!

2.title: Class Picture Day
2.plot: It's Class Picture Day at Mutt and Stuff and Calvin gets all the dogs dressed up in costumes for their puppy portrait. But the fun comes to a halt when two dogs want to dress like a pirate and there's only one pirate hat. Arrg.

3.title: Doggy Movin'
3.plot: When one of Calvin's students won't budge out of her new fancy doggy carrier, it's up to Calvin to find out why, and then get this doggy moving' and exercising!

4.title: Zippy's Birthday Bash
4.plot: While putting together a surprise birthday party for his best friend Zippy, Calvin can't figure out the perfect gift to make his buddy happy. Calvin's Dad, Cesar Millan, arrives and offers some great advice that helps Calvin find the perfect gift for the coolest dog on the planet.

5.title: A Pawsome Circus Show
5.plot: The dogs at Mutt and Stuff put on a circus; Calvin saves the day when a dog worries that his trick might not be good enough.

6.title: A Goldfish Opportunity
6.plot: Stuff tells Calvin that he wants a pet of his own to take care of, so Calvin gets Stuff a goldfish and teaches him what it takes to be a good pet owner. Stuff quickly learns that owning a pet is a big responsibility, and does whatever it takes to prove he can do it!

7.title: I Bark of Genie
7.plot: Zippy digs up a Genie lamp in the front yard and a Genie appears. After granting wishes to all of the dogs, Stuff wishes himself into a Genie and goes on a wishing spree. It's up to Calvin to put things back to normal when he gets turned into Zippy, and Zippy gets turned into Calvin.

8.title: Cloudy with a Chance of Accidents
8.plot: The class can't wait to go outside and see Zippy's new trick, but their plans get washed away when it starts raining. When Calvin switches plans and sets up a day of indoor doggy fun, one of the dogs has an accident.

9.title: Doggy Dino
9.plot: The costumes for Mutt and Stuff's doggy dinosaur costume party have not arrived yet; the class has an encounter with a real dinosaur.

10.title: Lady Woof Woof
10.plot: The doggy Rock Star Lady Woof Woof is visiting today! Stuff is her biggest fan and tries everything to make the doggy diva like him. When Lady Woof Woof and her personal handler, Doug E. Walker, arrive Stuff does his best to be a helpful pup for his new friends. Unfortunately, Stuff keeps comically messing up in his attempts. Calvin helps Stuff learn that it's okay to make mistakes, and that he doesn't have to change who his is for someone to like him.

11.title: The Fast & the Furriest
11.plot: Vroom Vroom! It's Race Day at Mutt & Stuff and Calvin has invited race dog extraordinaire Mario Bonedretti to join in on the racing fun. The dogs learn a thing or two about playing by the rules when it's revealed that Mario may not be the rule abiding champion he's made out to be.

12.title: Get Along Little Piggy
12.plot: Today there's a new student at Mutt & Stuff, and he oinks instead of barks - he's Skippity Boo the pig! The dogs and Skippity Boo have a ton of fun playing and having a hoedown doggy dance party!

13.title: Veterinary Loves Company
13.plot: To get one of his nervous dogs calm before a vet visit, Calvin plays a series of fun and calming games. But it turns out there is an even bigger and fluffier problem ahead - Stuff has to go to the vet too!

14.title: Achey Breaky Bark
14.plot: It's a cowboy-themed day when a country-pop singer comes to Mutt & Stuff with a scraggily dog she found on the road. Calvin and the class help get the pooch ready to be adopted, but the little dog melts the singer's heart, and she ends up adopting him into her country-pop cowboy family.

15.title: Ninja Dog
15.plot: It's Ninja Day at Mutt & Stuff! Calvin gets all of the dogs dressed up in ninja clothes to practice their skills, with the help of a super special ninja master!

16.title: Take Me to Your Pack Leader
16.plot: Calvin welcomes an extra special visitor to Mutt & Stuff who is truly out of this world An alien doggy named Wagoid from the Planet Snyf has traveled through space to see what makes Mutt & Stuff the greatest dog school in the galaxy. When Stuff accidentally breaks Wagoid's ship, the entire class chips in to help get their new space friend home. Wagoid realizes that Mutt & Stuff is a special place because the whole pack always sticks together to help each other out.

17.title: Skate Doggin'
17.plot: The dogs are going to the Big Skateboard Festival! Cuddles is nervous, because he's never set paw on a skateboard before! Calvin and the class help Cuddles overcome his nervousness by taking baby steps towards his goal.

18.title: Game of Bones
18.plot: Calvin is busy helping Grumbles get over his fear of participating in the Doggy Olympics. Fortunately, Calvin's younger cousin Marco is visiting, and he volunteers to help watch the rest of the dogs while Calvin works with Grumbles. Things get slapstick silly when Marco keeps messing up, causing disaster after comedic disaster. Cesar then arrives with Rex Javelin, a top doggy athlete who happens to be in a wheelchair. He's a dog athlete super star. With Calvin's guidance, the brave dog inspires both Grumbles and Macro to believe in themselves and achieve their very ...

19.title: Mutt & Stuff Express
19.plot: Mutt & Stuff is having an open house to give kids a tour of the school. So many kids show up that Calvin and the dogs have to build a train to carry everyone. Trouble arises though when all the dogs want to do the same job and be the conductor.

20.title: Cleo Kibble
20.plot: While preparing for the Big Mutt & Stuff Picnic, Calvin forgets snack time and breaks the Bow Wow Chow Snack machine trying to speed it up! Calvin calls Cleo Kibble to come fix the machine.

21.title: Dogs on a Plane
21.plot: The class are going on a vacation to Hawaii, and it's also their first time on an airplane! Calvin and a friendly flight attendant help teach the dogs about proper travel etiquette, the Mutt & Stuff way!

22.title: Sherdog Bones
22.plot: There's a new student at Mutt & Stuff. Mr. Shades little brother "Junior Shades" is joining the school. And on his first day, he loses his sunglasses! Calvin and the dogs must become doggy detectives to track down the shades.

23.title: Princess & the Cone
23.plot: It's Knights and Castles day at Mutt & Stuff, when the dogs get to dress up like it's the medieval times! But poor Princess Pickles, the fanciest dog in the land, has to wear a cone all day! Doctor's orders

24.title: Have a Very Mutty Christmas
24.plot: Mutt and Stuff is decorated for Christmas with a winter wonderland theme; Phil the snow dog visits and it begins to snow.

25.title: H.R. Pufnstuf Visits Mutt & Stuff
25.plot: Stuff's Uncle H.R. Pufnstuf is coming to visit Mutt & Stuff! Stuff wants to make sure everything is perfect for Pufnstuf's special visit, and he goes a bit overboard in an attempt to impress his favorite uncle.

26.title: Super Doggy Adoption
26.plot: A superhero flies into Mutt and Stuff with his potential new sidekick. An older dog named Awesome Doggy.

27.title: Welcome Noodles!
27.plot: Mutt & Stuff has a new class pet, and he's the cutest, littlest mouse named "Noodles Magoo!" Calvin and the class do their best to include the tiny mouse in their doggy activities.

28.title: Lights! Camera! Bark!
28.plot: A famous director comes to Mutt and Stuff to direct a movie with all of the dogs.

29.title: Amusement Bark
29.plot: Calvin takes the dogs to an Amusement Park, and Stuff has to learn patience while he waits for the big roller coaster ride!

30.title: Gabi's Groom-A-Thon
30.plot: Gabi Groomer wants to set a world record for washing the most dogs on a single day, so Calvin and the dogs build a giant automated dog-washing machine.

31.title: World Pup
31.plot: It's Soccer Day, and all the dogs put on uniforms to play in the big game! Then little Pixie scores the winning goal!

32.title: Goat in 60 Seconds!
32.plot: While at the Fun Farm Festival, Calvin's friend Jimmy Jasper asks Stuff to watch his prize-winning goat, but he immediately loses him! The pack works together to catch the goat just in time for the "Cutest Goat Contest".

33.title: Puppy Pirates
33.plot: Aaargh, matey! A real life pirate comes to Mutt & Stuff, looking for treasure!

34.title: Fire Dogs
34.plot: Fireman Fred and his firedog Dotti arrive in a real firetruck to teach Mutt & Stuff about fire safety!

35.title: Ruffin' It Camping
35.plot: Calvin takes all the dogs on a fun camping trip, where they set up tents, tell spooky stories, and sing doggy campfire songs!

36.title: Sick as a Dog
36.plot: When Calvin isn't feeling well, Cousin Marco takes over at Mutt and Stuff. Then he and the dogs try everything they can to make Calvin feel better.

37.title: Dinner with Cesar
37.plot: Calvin and the dogs make a surprise special dinner for Cesar to show how much they appreciate him.

38.title: Ba-a-a-ack to School!
38.plot: The class gets quite a surprise when two sheep wander into the school, and Calvin and the dogs have to figure out how to get them back home!

39.title: Dogs in Space
39.plot: When Marco visits to play catch with Rocket, he bounces a super bouncy ball too high, and it lands on the moon! Then Calvin, Marco, and the dogs build a spaceship to fly to the moon!

40.title: Pool Party
40.plot: It's super hot outside, so Calvin takes all the dogs on a field trip to an indoor pool park!

imdb.title: Mutt & Stuff
plot: Set in a unique school for dogs, the series stars Calvin Millan and his dad, Cesar, interacting with a cast of both real dogs and puppets at a canine school called Mutt and Stuff.::Anonymous
